All Known Implementing Classes:
BeaconProperties, CameraProperties, CameraTemplateProperties, CameraVidSourceOrderPanel, ControllerForm, DetectorPanel, DeviceDeployForm, DMSProperties, GateArmArrayProperties, GateArmDispatcher, LaneMarkingProperties, LCSArrayProperties, LcsDispatcher, LocationPanel, MeterDispatcher, ParkingAreaDispatcher, ParkingAreaProperties, PlanDispatcher, PlayListProperties, PropLocation, PropLocation, PropRwis, R_NodeLocationPanel, R_NodeSetupPanel, RampMeterProperties, SignConfigProperties, SignDetailProperties, SonarObjectForm, TagReaderProperties, UserPanel, WeatherSensorProperties
public interface ProxyView<T extends SonarObject>
An interface for watching proxy objects. These methods will be called on the event dispatch thread (EDT).
Author:
Douglas Lau
